to the story that my boobs

00:16.366 --> 00:18.833
be the last things to turn ape.

00:21.504 --> 00:24.506
It's sweet that he thinks
there's a story.

00:24.508 --> 00:27.141
Oh, and there's not even
a bathroom on set.

00:27.143 --> 00:29.410
I have to go to the gas station
across the street.

00:29.412 --> 00:31.346
I mean, I was dressed like
half an ape

00:31.348 --> 00:34.408
