professional opinion,

00:44.461 --> 00:46.327
which of these areas
do you think

00:46.329 --> 00:47.428
is the most promising?

00:47.430 --> 00:49.697
Huh, well, I-I think
there's some

00:49.699 --> 00:52.133
really innovative stuff
going on in dark matter.

00:52.135 --> 00:53.801
That's helpful.

00:56.639 --> 00:58.540
Okay. Of these four areas...

00:58.542 --> 00:59.674
PENNY:
Sheldon!

00:59.676 --> 01:01.376
What did we say about
being a nicer friend?

01:01.378 --> 01:02.777
Thank you.

01:02.779 --> 01:05.880
