Said it was stupid.

01:20.229 --> 01:21.696
Yeah. Sounds like me.

01:22.665 --> 01:23.932
Come on, Sheldon.
What do you say?

01:23.934 --> 01:26.834
All right.
I officially reinstate

01:26.836 --> 01:28.169
Anything Can Happen Thursday.

01:28.171 --> 01:30.138
Great! What do,
what do you want to do?

01:30.140 --> 01:31.472
