if she took her medicine.

03:46.450 --> 03:48.450
You know, when Cinnamon
won't take her medicine,

03:48.452 --> 03:50.152
I hide it in a piece of cheese.

03:50.154 --> 03:51.987
Good idea.
We can wrap the pill in cheese,

03:51.989 --> 03:53.021
