04:21.485 --> 04:22.517
You hate this stuff.

04:22.519 --> 04:24.452
I do, but for some reason,
Emily loves it

04:24.454 --> 04:26.354
and wants to watch it
with me tomorrow, so...

04:26.356 --> 04:27.556
I thought if
I start with you first,

04:27.558 --> 04:30.258
