04:59.622 --> 05:02.090
So, we're just randomly
choosing a restaurant

05:02.092 --> 05:03.525
without researching it online?

05:03.527 --> 05:04.359
Yep.

05:04.361 --> 05:05.927
Great.

05:05.929 --> 05:08.430
You know, this is how Anything
Can Happen Thursday turns into

05:08.432 --> 05:10.165
