(moans)

07:29.634 --> 07:30.768
What's wrong?

07:30.770 --> 07:33.637
I don't understand my food.

07:34.939 --> 07:39.009
Chinese noodles with
Korean barbecue...

07:39.011 --> 07:41.445
in a taco.

07:43.248 --> 07:45.115
It's fusion.

07:45.117 --> 07:47.618
Well, my mother would
lock her car doors

07:47.620 --> 07:51.522
