"Your warm and fun-loving nature
delights those around you."

11:04.416 --> 11:06.450
Oh, try again.
(clears her throat)

11:08.987 --> 11:11.455
(loud thudding on TV)

11:11.457 --> 11:13.857
(creaking on TV)

11:13.859 --> 11:15.125
(movie stops)

11:15.127 --> 11:16.493
(clears his throat)

11:17.328 --> 11:19.596
Let me get this straight.

11:19.598 --> 11:22.232
So, he kills this girl's father,

11:22.234 --> 11:24.434
cuts off the guy's face,

11:24.436 --> 11:26.536
and is wearing it as a mask

11:26.538 --> 11:29.406
while he makes out with her.

11:29.408 --> 11:31.308
I'm just gonna say it.

11:31.310 --> 11:34.044
That's not okay.

11:35.880 --> 11:37.781
Why can't I be in a relationship

11:37.783 --> 11:40.684
with a girl
who likes <i>The Sound of Music?</i>

11:40.686 --> 11:44.121
