in the relationship

11:44.123 --> 11:46.323
who likes <i>The Sound of Music.</i>

11:47.158 --> 11:49.359
(ringtone playing)

11:50.561 --> 11:52.996
Hey, Penny. What's up?

11:54.065 --> 11:56.233
No, Bernie's working late.

11:58.069 --> 12:00.470
Really?

12:00.472 --> 12:02.205
Thanks for telling me.

12:02.207 --> 12:04.975
What?

12:04.977 --> 12:08.111
I'm having sex with a Catholic
schoolgirl tonight.

12:08.113 --> 12:10.280
(laughs)

12:12.383 --> 12:14.017
(Penny gasps)

12:14.019 --> 12:16.453
