13:03.369 --> 13:05.969
Oh, no. I mean, this
is weird right now.

13:05.971 --> 13:07.337
(phone chimes)

13:07.339 --> 13:09.005
Oh.

13:09.007 --> 13:10.507
Ah, it's Penny.

13:10.509 --> 13:11.842
